(16296, 'Cibaprazon 1 gm powder for injection i.m/i.v vial', 'سيبابرازون 1 جم فيال', '', '12', 'Cefoperazone', 'Kahira > modern office for import', 'Injection', 'حقن', '', 'Antibiotic.cephalosporin.third-generation', '1 gm', 'Indicated for the treatment of following infections caused by susceptible bacteria:[label]
